18:T84a,<p>Discover the iconic Apple iPhone 3G, a device that changed the future of mobile technology with its elegant design and smart functionality. Crafted with a smooth curved body and a premium minimalist finish, the iPhone 3G delivers both style and comfort in your hand.</p><p>Powered by fast 3G connectivity, this smartphone offers improved web browsing, email access, and online experiences compared to earlier mobile devices. Its vibrant touchscreen display provides a smooth and user-friendly interface, making navigation simple and enjoyable for everyday tasks.</p><p>The iPhone 3G combines essential features including music playback, internet browsing, messaging, maps, and access to the revolutionary App Store — allowing users to personalize their phone with a variety of applications and games.</p><p>Designed for people who appreciate simplicity and innovation, the iPhone 3G remains one of the most influential smartphones ever created. Whether for collection, nostalgia, or basic smart functionality, it represents a milestone in modern mobile history.</p><h3>Key Features</h3><ol><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Elegant curved and lightweight design</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Responsive multi-touch display</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Fast 3G internet connectivity</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Built-in music and media player</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Access to apps and mobile games</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Smooth and intuitive iOS experience</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Integrated camera for everyday photos</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Wi-Fi and Bluetooth support</li></ol><p>Perfect for collectors, vintage tech enthusiasts, or users seeking a classic smartphone experience with legendary Apple design</p>d:["$","div",null,{"className":"p-2 md:p-4 min-h-screen","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 md:mb-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800","children":"Products"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1","children":"Manage Products"}]]}],["$","$L15",null,{"href":"product/add","children":["$","button",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 px-3 md:px-5 py-2 md:py-2.5 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-md hover:scale-105 transition text-sm","children":[["$","$L16",null,{"ref":"$undefined","iconNode":[["path",{"d":"M5 12h14","key":"1ays0h"}],["path",{"d":"M12 5v14","key":"s699le"}]],"className":"lucide-plus","size":16}],["$","span",null,{"className":"hidden sm:inline","children":"Add Product"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"sm:hidden","children":"Add"}]]}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"overflow-x-auto","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"min-w-full text-left border-collapse","children":[["$","thead",null,{"className":"bg-gray-50 border-b","children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"className":"px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Image"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Name"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Category"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Brand"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase track